y":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f937903fd7b12fbdded8004aed02e367f7e408","tid":1603774,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d35900d99f4107e13f3adc04c07b36f07d9870","tid":1603774,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a108d9c38f0dcf0e1f6df649cabf23c4824c54dc","tid":1603774,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:27:12.000Z","msg":"掘磚嘅你哋...點解唔一人一罐可樂？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e068b1a80c4c4e461b86866671ce23e887767ef9","tid":1603774,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:27:14.000Z","msg":"司令點揀出嚟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成件事好困難 <br />\n1. 鬼係有機會做司令<br />\n2. 司令落咗錯嘅決定會令成件事好易有目標地分化<br />\n<br />\n目前係一個瓶頸位但我對司令呢一點都仲係有少少保留"},{"pid":"e546a811860bb69521da359eac3469bb5f399f8e","tid":1603774,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bce01133a323472b0908a18f09d954e84367764","tid":1603774,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e068b1a80c4c4e461b86866671ce23e887767ef9","tid":1603774,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:27:14.000Z","msg":"司令點揀出嚟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成件事好困難 <br />\n1. 鬼係有機會做司令<br />\n2. 司令落咗錯嘅決定會令成件事好易有目標地分化<br />\n<br />\n目前係一個瓶頸位但我對司令呢一點都仲係有少少保留"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:29:14.000Z","msg":"毅進仔 邊有勇氣做司令<br />\n佢地混入我地已經好大壓力<br />\n<br />\n不過唔排除日後警察會進化到咁<br />\n短期內唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6f643cde5d44abd53da3dc34ff6474e8988773","tid":1603774,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c80249c5502c18f533c2b87c65dd58d07044b1b","tid":1603774,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf0c8f43adf699be65eb9b313fde6cf19564f6e","tid":1603774,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d5a97925badb1af54c19ff399a62dd08c22c5e","tid":1603774,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bce01133a323472b0908a18f09d954e84367764","tid":1603774,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e068b1a80c4c4e461b86866671ce23e887767ef9","tid":1603774,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:27:14.000Z","msg":"司令點揀出嚟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成件事好困難 <br />\n1. 鬼係有機會做司令<br />\n2. 司令落咗錯嘅決定會令成件事好易有目標地分化<br />\n<br />\n目前係一個瓶頸位但我對司令呢一點都仲係有少少保留"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:29:14.000Z","msg":"毅進仔 邊有勇氣做司令<br />\n佢地混入我地已經好大壓力<br />\n<br />\n不過唔排除日後警察會進化到咁<br />\n短期