\n自己既個人意見理應係要佔好少部分<br />\n<br />\n講到好紙上談兵 都係人力配套 同資源問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c024e201ec668492009e11c9eec9d88d092d98","tid":1603774,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}